```{r}
# load in libraries
package_list <- c("tidyverse", "vroom", "dplyr")

# load in packages
for (package_name in package_list) {
  if (!requireNamespace(package_name, quietly = TRUE)) {
    install.packages(package_name)
  }
  library(package_name, character.only = TRUE)
}

# load in data
df <- vroom("ddh.csv")
```
